    "body": "This ticket seems to duplicate trufflesuite/truffle#3467, so I'm going to close it in favour of that one. I'll do my best to capture any details here that aren't already covered by that issue.\r\n\r\nBy way of status report, trufflesuite/truffle#5222 was merged last week, and it will go out with the next Truffle release. That PR contains the core changes necessary to support TypeScript migrations, but I'd consider that version as being an initial \"beta\" release of the feature. We are still working on fleshing out the other details of the feature, including docs (trufflesuite/trufflesuite.com#1276), VSCode integration (#5368) and initial TypeScript migrations when running `truffle init` (#5369), etc.",
